===FCC=== * The FCC test report specifies the manufacturer of the device as ''Compal'' :(Compal Networking [KunShan]), however, the FCC photos show the board w/ :standard ''[[Arcadyan]]'' (in which [http://www.arcadyan.com/contentpage.aspx?type=infocontent&L2id=1&infoid=3 it appears] ''Compal'' has a [http://www.emsnow.com/newsarchives/archivedetails.cfm?ID=14039 significant stake]) :labels on it (model: Arcadyan WG6117EAC22-ASU)
*PCB in the FCC photos :''"RT-AC56U REV 1.60"'' is silkscreened on the (red) PCB :''"RT-AC56U REV 2.00"'' is silkscreened on the (blue) PCB
